    <item>
      <title>最高法院考虑允许设立宗教特许学校</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/supreme-court-to-consider-bid-to-allow-religious-charter-schools</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院接受了一场新的重大政教对决，同意考虑拥有公立特许学校的州是否在宪法上要求批准和资助宗教机构作为该计划的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/supreme-court-to-consider-bid-to-allow-religious-charter-schools</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 21:35:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢比奥与中国外长王毅通话强调“美国优先”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/marco-rubio-stresses-america-first-in-call-with-china-s-wang-yi</link>
      <description><![CDATA[长期对华鹰派的美国国务卿马尔科·卢比奥周五在与中国外交部长王毅的首次正式通话中表达了对北京对台湾采取胁迫行为以及在南海采取侵略行为的担忧，这一迹象表明中美关系可能陷入动荡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/marco-rubio-stresses-america-first-in-call-with-china-s-wang-yi</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 21:21:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普官员称，美国环保署将重新考虑加州的排放限制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/epa-revisiting-california-emissions-curbs-trump-official-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国政府在一份最高法院文件中表示，唐纳德·特朗普总统的环境保护署正在考虑撤销加利福尼亚州通过严格的汽车污染限制来应对气候变化的许可。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/epa-revisiting-california-emissions-curbs-trump-official-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 21:12:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大考虑设立新枢纽以应对可能出现的美国难民潮</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/canada-eyes-new-hub-to-handle-possible-refugee-surge-from-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着特朗普政府推进移民打击行动，加拿大计划设立一处中心，接待从美国穿越北部边境进入魁北克的移民。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/canada-eyes-new-hub-to-handle-possible-refugee-surge-from-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 21:10:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
